{
  "stem": "893.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I right away realized that-- that that was the day when they rounded up all the Jews, and-- and they took them to-- to a city, Sered.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That was the-- that was the city where they rounded up all the Jews from Slovakia, and they took them all to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I took the train back to [NON-ENGLISH], and I had no problem.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They checked my identity papers, and we came back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I came back to my brother, who was very upset, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Even though I went to work, I still felt, maybe I should go back, maybe.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But my friend-- and we decided, well, we wouldn't help them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Maybe by staying out, we would-- we would be-- to go into their hands, we still had time, we felt.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So we stayed out there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We still wanted to pursue the-- our plan to go back to Hungary, since the situation in Hungary was much better than here.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There was-- there were no Jews anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The only Jews that were there were in hiding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we had no contact with those Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Well, you know, we tried to-- to do whatever we can.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Even-- we had even money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We had dollars.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But as long as the Jews were in Slovakia, we could change the dollars to Slovakian currency, but we couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "My father took some money with him, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I'm sure the Germans got them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And so we decided-- we knew about-- we knew that in that village, there was one of the farmers was hiding an automobile, a new automobile that belonged to the Croatian ambassador to Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So we clinged to any straw at that point.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
